&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; Maintain good housekeeping of the vessel and ensure that all essential victualling has taken place.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
