&lt;p&gt;B2&lt;span&gt; B5 B8 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;69%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Duty 8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt; handle the vessel both with and against the tide in high traffic density and amongst fixed hazards such as bridges whilst utilizing common propulsion systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td width=&quot;30%&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;K3&lt;span&gt; K4 K8 K9 K10 K11 K12 K16 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
