&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mandatory qualification 5: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;Diploma in Maritime Studies: Rivers, Inland Waterways and Limited Distances to Sea – SQA 601/0021/7&lt;/p&gt;
